{
  "1796580": {
    "name": "Sorry We're Closed",
    "steam_appid": 1796580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/332544d33141c74d04daee86085c8a75.avif?t=1771515109\" width=780 height=268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Sorry We're Closed》</strong>融合了怀旧的生存恐怖与全新的战斗体验，采用氛围感十足的环境搭配固定视角和刺激的街机风格第一人称射击。通过收集物品和管理资源来帮助米歇尔求生。喜欢经典生存恐怖体验的玩家还可选择坦克式操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >古怪离奇的霓虹色彩生存恐怖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随时日无多的米歇尔一起战斗，打破求爱的强大魔王施加于她的诅咒。米歇尔所在的伦敦区熙熙攘攘，在她追寻自由、摆脱早逝命运的过程中，为这里好奇的居民提供帮助（或制造阻碍！）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/fb8b096602375a3f0f88ce54cc524d5b.poster.avif?t=1771515109\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/fb8b096602375a3f0f88ce54cc524d5b.webm?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/fb8b096602375a3f0f88ce54cc524d5b.mp4?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >米歇尔一半时间在危机四伏的恶魔世界艰难求生，另一半在与邻里的本地人结识交往。每个人都在与自己内心的恶魔作斗争，而你可以通过米歇尔为他们指引方向。海量角色可供互动，通过RPG风格的对话走向多种结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/41d20383820f6f85cb2be38f6dbe0ffe.poster.avif?t=1771515109\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/41d20383820f6f85cb2be38f6dbe0ffe.webm?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/41d20383820f6f85cb2be38f6dbe0ffe.mp4?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹指间开启第三只眼……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >米歇尔获得了第三只眼的力量，让她能够窥视不同世界，了解她周围的隐秘生灵。剥离世界边界来揭晓秘密和破解谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/abb6009d963f245d2f3af1ca0fa473bc.poster.avif?t=1771515109\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/abb6009d963f245d2f3af1ca0fa473bc.webm?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/abb6009d963f245d2f3af1ca0fa473bc.mp4?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第三只眼将成为米歇尔对战危险对手时最强大的工具，尤其是在头目遭遇战中！它可以揭示恶魔的弱点，从而造成最大伤害。通过完美的弱点连击干掉敌人还可为终极大招充能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/6978cdf7534105c35a6c762e3c482c53.poster.avif?t=1771515109\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/6978cdf7534105c35a6c762e3c482c53.webm?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/6978cdf7534105c35a6c762e3c482c53.mp4?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天使与恶魔的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入神魔的世界中一步步展开米歇尔的故事，通过战斗打破求爱的强大恶魔施加于她的诅咒。了解成为天使或者恶魔意味着什么，二者融合时又会发生什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/0ff19a1935519cac089ccc5476b5f9df.poster.avif?t=1771515109\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/0ff19a1935519cac089ccc5476b5f9df.webm?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796580/extras/0ff19a1935519cac089ccc5476b5f9df.mp4?t=1771515109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事支持多个结局，不同的选择将会提供新的机遇去回避或接受魔王的诱惑，从而影响米歇尔的命运。米歇尔干预得越多，她周围人的生活也会随之发生越大的变化。能够改变的并非只有她一个人的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果米歇尔敢给她的地狱犬手枪上膛，大胆闯入恶魔世界，或许她能找到办法夺回自己的命运。</p>",
